data.text:
Large capacity, Max to 2042Wh

 High-power Solar Charging, it supports solar panel charging from 120W to 1000W.

 Bi-Directional Inverter Technology, With AC input up to 2000W, the power station can be fully charged in around 1 hour.

 Ultra-low Standby Power Consumption, the power station automatically monitors its working status and switches on and off standby mode in accordance.

 Six Charging and Discharging Protection Modes of BMS.
